# --- vault-specific ---
# Emitted run artifacts are regenerated by running the scripts. Commit a
# curated snapshot if you want the dashboard to render without a local run,
# otherwise keep the live tree out of version control:
#   Chiron/artifacts/
# manifest.json is a generated index; regenerate with build_manifest.py.
# Uncomment the next two lines to treat them as generated (not committed):
# Chiron/artifacts/
# Chiron/manifest.json

